{"tid":1566184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[認真討論] 歌可以唱 但正經野一樣要做","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:51:46.000Z","uid":117737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e50927d04df9b7892272fbf8f68ada1eeff209c5","tid":1566184,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"我知有好多人屌唱歌，但唱歌可以激勵士氣、團結人心，唔好睇少唱歌威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同時一樣要跟貼市況走勢，特別是美國《香港民主及人權法案》<br />\n一定是靠美國食糊，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔通靠共產黨／仆街港共政權自己讓步呀？</span></span></strong><br />\n我地今次輸，一定俾共產黨清算到仆街－我地無退路、<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無退路呀係！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nPetition 要簽既繼續簽、對外國施加壓力是重點！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"6b9f1ef532d4d3b16aad0f2fed57dc341fbade24","tid":1566184,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a9b0bd666985d7d61210bd3120dc043c9bade48e","tid":1566184,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"3614bf5b7baf1039463c151cd7b128acaa1056f6","tid":1566184,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a071f9a841f26c5c48c96feb6749b1e04b5c0807","tid":1566184,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f8496c9832e3029e3194a05ae94ff69a9285af70","tid":1566184,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"p