1lGY</a><br />\n圖：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B2JgR5dBlx8/?igshid=1jyzbuqriofhy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2JgR5dBlx8%2F%3Figshid%3D1jyzbuqriofhy&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=933407cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2JgR5dBlx8%2F%3Figshid%3D1jyzbuqriofhy&h=8b995ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B2JgR5dBlx8/?igshid=1jyzbuqriofhy</a><br />\n波蘭人又拍片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y3iFiSiJYX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy3iFiSiJYX4&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=1dc59bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y3iFiSiJYX4</a><br />\n德國人直頭比我地嘅手足做難民<br />\n仲有好多其他不能盡數<br />\n唔該見到就留返個言多謝返佢地 長期作戰 聚人心唔係一下就夠<br />\n韓文：지지해주셔서 감사합니다. 5대요구, 하나도 빠져선 안된다.<br />\n1. 송환법 완전히 철폐<br />\n2. 폭동 규정 철회<br />\n3. 체포된 시위자 공소철회 및 무죄석방<br />\n4. 공권력 남용 강경 진압에 나선 경찰 문책<br />\n5. 행정명령으로 국회를 해산시켜 즉각 행정장관과 입법회 보통 선거 도입<br />\n德文: Herzlichen Dank f&uuml;r all Ihre Unterst&uuml;tzung. F&uuml;nf Hauptforderungen, niemand weniger! <br />\n1. Allgemeines Wahlrecht f&uuml;r den Regierungschef und auch Legislativrat. <br />\n2. Die Freilassung von festgenommenen Demonstranten. <br />\n3. Die Einrichtung eines unabh&auml;ngigen Untersuchungsausschusses. <br />\n4. Die R&uuml;cknahme der Deklarierung der Proteste als Aufruhr. <br />\n5. Die komplette R&uuml;cknahme des Auslieferungsgesetzes.<br />\n<br />\n中英：&ldquo;Five Core Demands, All or None.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\nFormally Withdrawal (without any ambiguity) of the Extradition Bill<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\nWithdrawal of the characterization of the all related conflicts as &ldquo;riot&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\nDismiss all charges made against demonstrators who protested against the Bill;<br />\nGuarantee no further charges will be made.<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\nAccountability for Police Abuse of Authority and Excessive Force<br />\n(Set up an independent commission of inquiry to conduct impartial investigation).<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\nDissolve the Legislative Council with an executive order;<br />\nImmediately implement Genuine Universal Suffrage <br />\n(direct election both the Chief Executive and the Legislative Council)."},{"pid":"c18cb1e4752ce55f9cd66869d6f7b1c2171a350c","tid":1566184,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad1dd33b538ab4c89cd3c6e8b8155880cdac639","tid":1566184,"uid":93519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"即刻出街貼文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6whTkHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6whTkHK.jpg&h=1faef575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvHoHV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvHoHV7.jpg&h=7fa49e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇諗過文宜可以咁貼？<br />\n<br />\n-五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n-政府施暴，市民不是暴徒<br />\n-15/9銅鑼灣東角道見<br />\n-721，警察唔見人<br />\n-831，警察打死人<br />\n-新屋嶺，警察強姦少女<br />\n-多謝勇武，絕不割席<br />\n-不割席，不篤灰<br />\n-兄弟爬山，共同努力<br />\n-不唱k,唱文宣<br />\n-不玩嘉年華，做行動召集"},{"pid":"655a1b99c87a90308e1a45dca161ffe7fa46a63d","tid":1566184,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"歌可以唱 但正經野要做<br />\n唔係嘅話外國戰線會以為香港已經冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}